"title": "5813: conceit",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5813",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A state of pride arising out of an overestimation of one's own ability, possessions or importance.</p>\n<h2>The definition of conceit</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:3\">GAL 6:3</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Examples of conceit</h2>\n<h3>In military strength</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:33-2Kgs18:35\">2KI 18:33–18:35</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:9\">EXO 15:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:42-1Sam17:44\">1SA 17:42–17:44</a></p>\n<h3>In the power of idols</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:15\">DAN 3:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:9-Acts8:10\">ACT 8:9–8:10</a></p>\n<h3>In personal abilities</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:33\">MAT 26:33</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:29\">MRK 14:29</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen16:4\">GEN 16:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs20:11\">1KI 20:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth5:10-Esth5:12\">EST 5:10–5:12</a></p>\n<h3>In false teaching</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:3-1Tim6:4\">1TI 6:3–6:4</a></strong></p>\n<h3>In possessions</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos12:8\">HOS 12:8</a></strong></p>\n<h3>In intellectual ability</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:7-Ps73:9\">PSA 73:7–73:9</a></strong></p>\n<h3>In national status</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa47:6-Isa47:8\">ISA 47:6–47:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa16:6\">ISA 16:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer48:29\">JER 48:29</a></p>\n<h2>God's response to conceit</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:28\">2SA 22:28</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:27-1Cor1:29\">1CO 1:27–1:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:12\">ISA 2:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa23:9\">ISA 23:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa47:8-Isa47:11\">ISA 47:8–47:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Obad1:3-Obad1:4\">OBA 1:3–1:4</a></p>\n<h2>Warnings against conceit</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:3\">PHP 2:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:7\">PRO 3:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:21\">ISA 5:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:23-Jer9:24\">JER 9:23–9:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:3\">ROM 12:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:16\">ROM 12:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:18-1Cor3:21\">1CO 3:18–3:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:7\">1CO 4:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor8:2\">1CO 8:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:26\">GAL 5:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:4\">2TI 3:4</a></p>\n<h2>The folly of conceit</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov26:12\">PRO 26:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:26\">PRO 28:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa16:6\">ISA 16:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos10:13-Hos10:14\">HOS 10:13–10:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:5\">JAS 3:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:16\">JAS 4:16</a></p>\n<h2>The danger of conceit for Christians</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:12\">1CO 10:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:25\">ROM 11:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:7\">2CO 12:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:6\">1TI 3:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:16\">1JN 2:16</a></p>\n<h2>Remedies for conceit</h2>\n<h3>Being aware of one's sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:9-Luke18:14\">LUK 18:9–18:14</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Being prepared to mix with the lowly</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:16\">ROM 12:16</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Considering others as being superior</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:3\">PHP 2:3</a></strong></p>",
